    <published>2022-04-12T11:31:38.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-04-13T03:28:43.591Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>最近发现自己在Python理论方面有很大的不足,具体体现为东西我会做,但是一旦问到概念性的东西,我就很难回答的完整,甚至于是自己都没有见过、用过一些基础的技术, 今天意识到这个问题:地基打不牢,面试地动山摇,因此决定特开一篇学习历程.md,以解决遇到一些基础的问题都答不上来这个情况.会记录一些见过或者没见过,自己觉得简单或者较难的概念问题.</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;hello world&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><span id="more"></span><h4 id="字符串"><a href="#字符串" class="headerlink" title="字符串"></a>字符串</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 按步长输出字符</span></span><br><span class="line">str_a = <span class="string">&quot;abcdefg&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(str_a[::<span class="number">2</span>])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="built_in">print</span>(str_a[::<span class="number">2</span>])</span><br><span class="line">aceg</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># python3 中bool是int的子类,也就是说True=1, False=0</span></span><br><span class="line">实际操作起来就是<span class="literal">True</span>+<span class="number">1</span>=<span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">一个/ 除法获得浮点数</span><br><span class="line">两个 // 除法获得整数</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="列表-List"><a href="#列表-List" class="headerlink" title="列表 List []"></a>列表 List []</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">+是列表的连接运算符 *是重复操作符</span><br><span class="line">表现为</span><br><span class="line">listA + listB = listAlistB</span><br><span class="line">listA * <span class="number">2</span> = listAlistA</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="元组-tuple"><a href="#元组-tuple" class="headerlink" title="元组 tuple()"></a>元组 tuple()</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 元组与列表相似 但元组内容不可改变 且元组是用()表示的 元组内元素可以用索引</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="集合set"><a href="#集合set" class="headerlink" title="集合set{}"></a>集合set{}</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 基本功能是进行成员关系测试?和删除重复元素。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 使用方法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span>() 或者 &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">剩下的基本与<span class="built_in">list</span>一样 但是可以用&amp;来判断两集合中相同的元素 /来判断不同时存在的元素</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="字典-Dictionary"><a href="#字典-Dictionary" class="headerlink" title="字典 Dictionary {}"></a>字典 Dictionary {}</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">字典是一种映射类型,字典中的元素由键来存取,而不是通过下标索引,键必须唯一</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 定义一个字典</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">dict</span> = &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 传入键值</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">dict</span>[<span class="string">&#x27;key&#x27;</span>] = <span class="string">&#x27;value&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 输出所有key</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">dict</span>.keys()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">dict</span>.values()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="import"><a href="#import" class="headerlink" title="import"></a>import</h4><p>直接import 导入的东西叫模块</p><p>from xxx import AAA 导入的AAA叫做函数</p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;最近发现自己在Python理论方面有很大的不足,具体体现为东西我会做,但是一旦问到概念性的东西,我就很难回答的完整,甚至于是自己都没有见过、用过一些基础的技术, 今天意识到这个问题:地基打不牢,面试地动山摇,因此决定特开一篇学习历程.md,以解决遇到一些基础的问题都答不上来这个情况.会记录一些见过或者没见过,自己觉得简单或者较难的概念问题.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight python&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;hello world&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    
